orks palerra pulse secure qualys inc tufin ubiqube verisign inc whitehat security and ziften fortinet also introduced the fortigate e gbits firewall which includes the new cp asic that takes on some processing tasks from the main cpu and was used in future fortigate releases other productsedit fortinet provides numerous other software and hardware products including more than one dozen other products for switching desktops voip services dns user authentication and other applications the companys fortianalyzer software offers reporting features for fortinet products including event logging security reporting and analysis forticlient is an endpoint security product for desktops phones and other devices forticlient vpn software was first released in april  the fortiguard antispam and the fortimail messaging security products were first released in february  fortimanager the companys software for data center security was first introduced in april  fortinet introduced its database security product family in  fortinets fortiswitch switching platforms were first introduced in  and its application delivery controllers in august  in october  fortinet released virtual software versions of its fortigate fortimanager fortianalyzer and fortimail appliances it updated the forticloud management system in august  a softwaredefined networking offering was introduced in september  fortinet produces and markets wireless versions of its fortigate product called fortiwifi which was first in march  fortinet introduced a new family of cloudbased wireless access points in august  the fortiddos product family was introduced in march  fortiguard also provide a visual output of global sample data collected from all fortigate appliances connected to the fortiguard labs databases the threat map is publicly available for sample data and can also be viewed specific to a single fortigate appliance within fortios operationsedit fortinet also runs the fortiguard labs internal security research team 